<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>My Shopify Store</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1 class="text-2xl">Welcome to My Shopify Store</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/collections/all">Shop</a></li>
                <li><a href="/pages/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/pages/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Featured Products</h2>
            <ul>
                {% for product in collections.frontpage.products limit:4 %}
                    <li>
                        <a href="{{ product.url }}">
                            <img src="{{ product.featured_image | img_url: 'medium' }}" alt="{{ product.title }}">
                            <h3>{{ product.title }}</h3>
                            <p>{{ product.price | money }}</p>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam auctor, nisl at lacinia tincidunt, velit nunc tincidunt nunc, id tincidunt nisl nunc auctor nunc.</p>
            <a href="/pages/about">Learn More</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; {{ 'now' | date: '%Y' }} My Shopify Store. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
